race.comment: MISS VEUVE (4) rounded up her rivals here last start to win with ease, bolting in by 1.3L in fine style as favourite. Makes the progression to a CL1 today but this doesn't look overly strong based on her latest effort. Can storm over the top to go back-to-back. VEXATIOUS ROSE (6) is a maiden racing up in grade today, though the mile looks right up her alley. She's been flying home from impossibly positions this time in. If Whiting can have her somewhere midfield from the good barrier, then she's right in this race. JAYASHREE (3) has been racing well without winning at Kalgoorlie, going around favourite in a CL2 most recently. This looks a good race on the back of that performance where she sat on the speed. Ticks a few boxes and can make her presence felt. BATTLE COMMANDER (1) is better than he showed last timeout and can return to form. AUTHORATIVE (2) is racing well and is not out of this.
